{"tid":1838323,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北美華人籌款 買醫療物資口罩送武漢","createTime":"2020-01-24T03:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T04:01:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1dbd2830885340437f102fef5b9dec63560e576","tid":1838323,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:38:25.000Z","msg":"武漢封城後，呼籲各界捐款及捐贈口罩等物資。一班在北美的華人積極響應，有人在網上發起眾籌，採購口罩運到武漢，以及統籌從北美地區運送物資經長沙等地送入武漢。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎大爆發，醫療物資極度缺乏，增加醫護人員感染風險。在微博上的帳戶「為武漢捐贈」表示，他們是一班在美華人自發組織的公益小組，發起由北美地區向武漢和周邊城市捐贈物資的活動。在美國組織和採購籌得的醫療物資，經航空和火車運送到武漢。<br />\n<br />\n他們在美國時間周二發起籌款後，即日達標，捐款用來購買一萬個外科口罩，周三由北京送到武漢5間醫院。第二批24萬個口罩和1.5萬件防護服，預計也會在這一兩天內送達。他們目前暫時停止接受捐款，會集中處理運送在北美購買和收集到的物資。<br />\n<br />\n他們目前已按照職能分開6個小組，分別是：負責總體協調的工作組、負責搜集中國國內資訊，包括各醫院所需的國內醫院組、負責募捐的國外募集組、負責北美當地寄送安排的國際快遞組、負責在武漢接貨分發至醫院的快遞運輸組，以及負責款項流向的物資統計財務組。<br />\n<br />\n北美有心人士購買醫療物資後，可以寄送到位於洛杉磯、三藩市和紐約的指定倉庫。他們再安排分批空運到長沙和廣州，經由當地的義工團隊，通過綠色通道運送到武漢的醫院前線或武漢衛健委。<br />\n<br />\n為方便分類和清關，他們建議捐贈的物資盡量統一型號，例如同一型號口罩和防護服，而且以機構和團體方式，集合較大量的物資寄送。目前不接受個人的定向物資運送要求。詳情可參考：為武漢捐款及捐贈醫療物資指南<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200124/large/1579833174_1b0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200124%2Flarge%2F1579833174_1b0a.jpg&h=a67c3702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200124/large/1579833174_2dc7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200124%2Flarge%2F1579833174_2dc7.png&h=978baea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200124/JSW32ETTAGRCKRSIO43CWJ5CVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200124%2FJSW32ETTAGRCKRSIO43CWJ5CVI%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=70abba76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200124%2FJSW32ETTAGRCKRSIO43CWJ5CVI%2F&h=8531c490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200124/JSW32ETTAGRCKRSIO43CWJ5CVI/</a>"},{"pid":"5f9bed4ded12b95fe3cd7258ee6a9b138cd9bfeb","tid":1838323,"uid":3513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"落格落左幾多？"},{"pid":"304a18ba584cefc7332f097ec8b0fb4196b6cdbf","tid":1838323,"uid":161726,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"藥房入貨都多過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e893cc64d0cef5161100c1cae46fb2e794dfe2a","tid":1838323,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f9bed4ded12b95fe3cd7258ee6a9b138cd9bfeb","tid":1838323,"uid":3513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"落格落左幾多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"運曬落嚟香港黑心藥房再賣返上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd8d598ab992488649b52d3b5327667efd22c16","tid":1838323,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f9bed4ded12b95fe3cd7258ee6a9b138cd9bfeb","tid":1838323,"uid":3513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"落格落左幾多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"地方官收左唔派<br />\n<br />\n比晒屋企人拎出去開鋪炒口罩發国難財<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6a80d7cc8c3de876c9ae619e67c99c4bc39801","tid":1838323,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"又話係強國 做咩要靠人捐"},{"pid":"5f0906bb84b8294d5c5ce73e73984247645bcfc9","tid":1838323,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:43:42.000Z","msg":"醫療物資有咩用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t26cuKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft26cuKb.jpg&h=2d13c7ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7018960f0